title: Virgil_Introduction
---
"Have pity on me, whatever you may be, a shade, a man." #card:Dante #line:0fd5718 

"Not man; I once was man. Both of my parents came from Lombardy, and both claimed Mantua as native city. I was a poet, born under false and lying gods." #line:081e541 

"Could you be Virgil? The-" #card:Dante #line:06637f1  

"We cannot talk now, the beasts will get to us, let's get moving!" #line:05e67b5 

